# Title: DeviceCredentialDeployment Execution
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the execution of DeviceCredentialDeployment to hide a process from view.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_device_credential_deployment.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

Image="*\\DeviceCredentialDeployment.exe"